<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>ARIA Corp. | 인증 포털</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Share+Tech+Mono&family=Orbitron:wght@400;700;900&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #030810;
      --panel: #050f1a;
      --border: #0d3a5c;
      --accent: #00d4ff;
      --accent2: #ff4444;
      --text: #a8d8ea;
      --muted: #3a6b8a;
      --glow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,212,255,0.4);
    }

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(0,212,255,0.025) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,212,255,0.025) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 40px 40px;
      animation: gs 25s linear infinite;
    }

    @keyframes gs { to { transform: translateY(40px); } }

    body::after {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 2px, rgba(0,0,0,0.1) 2px, rgba(0,0,0,0.1) 4px);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .login-wrap {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 10;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 420px;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .logo-area {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .logo {
      font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      text-shadow: var(--glow);
      letter-spacing: 6px;
    }

    .logo span { color: #ff4444; }

    .logo-sub {
      font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    .login-panel {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: rgba(5,15,26,0.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      padding: 40px;
      position: relative;
    }

    .login-panel::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--accent), transparent);
    }

    .panel-title {
      font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .panel-title::after {
      content: '';
      flex: 1;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
    }

    .error-box {
      background: rgba(255,68,68,0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,68,68,0.4);
      padding: 10px 14px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--accent2);
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    label {
      display: block;
      font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    input {
      width: 100%;
      background: rgba(0,212,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 12px 14px;
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }

    input:focus {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(0,212,255,0.15);
    }

    input::placeholder { color: var(--muted); opacity: 0.5; }

    .submit-btn {
      width: 100%;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #000;
      border: none;
      padding: 14px;
      font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-top: 8px;
      clip-path: polygon(6px 0%, 100% 0%, calc(100% - 6px) 100%, 0% 100%);
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .submit-btn:hover {
      background: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(0,212,255,0.5);
    }

    .back-link {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
    }

    .back-link a {
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .back-link a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

    .corner { position: absolute; width: 10px; height: 10px; border-color: var(--accent); border-style: solid; opacity: 0.6; }
    .corner.tl { top: -1px; left: -1px; border-width: 2px 0 0 2px; }
    .corner.tr { top: -1px; right: -1px; border-width: 2px 2px 0 0; }
    .corner.bl { bottom: -1px; left: -1px; border-width: 0 0 2px 2px; }
    .corner.br { bottom: -1px; right: -1px; border-width: 0 2px 2px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="login-wrap">
  <div class="logo-area">
    <div class="logo">ARIA<span>.</span>CORP</div>
    <div class="logo-sub">INTERNAL AUTHENTICATION PORTAL</div>
  </div>

  <div class="login-panel">
    <div class="corner tl"></div>
    <div class="corner tr"></div>
    <div class="corner bl"></div>
    <div class="corner br"></div>

    <div class="panel-title">// 계정 정보 확인</div>

    <% if (error === 'invalid') { %>
    <div class="error-box">⚠ 인증 실패 - 유효하지 않은 계정입니다.</div>
    <% } else if (error === 'auth') { %>
    <div class="error-box">⚠ 접근 거부 — 인증이 필요합니다</div>
    <% } %>

    <form method="POST" action="/login">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label>USER ID</label>
        <input type="text" name="username" placeholder="identifier" autocomplete="off" required>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label>PASSPHRASE</label>
        <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="••••••••" required>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">시스템 접근</button>
    </form>

    <div class="back-link">
      <a href="/">← 브리핑으로 돌아가기</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
